frus:attachment.p:
The Government of Cuba has failed to cooperate in arrangements to
                                ensure that all offensive weapons are removed from and not
                                reintroduced into Cuba;

3. To inform the Security Council of the United Nations of this
                                resolution in accordance with Article 54 of the Charter of the
                                United Nations;

Noting with satisfaction that certain
                                offensive weapons and related facilities have been removed from
                                Cuba;

Believing further that steps should be taken
                                to safeguard against the future reintroduction of offensive weapons
                                in Cuba;
